{"id": "art-202910", "label": "Art. 202910", "title": "Art. 202910: Renunţarea mandatarului", "slug": "art-202910", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1519411056\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1058\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1519411056\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 2029<sup>10</sup>:\nRenun&#355;area mandatarului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1556899837\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1057\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1556899837\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Mandatarul nu poate renun&#355;a la mandatul s&#259;u\nf&#259;r&#259; s&#259; î&#351;i substituie o alt&#259; persoan&#259; în\nexecutarea mandatului, dac&#259; mandantul l-a autorizat în mod expres, sau\nf&#259;r&#259; s&#259; solicite instan&#355;ei de tutel&#259; instituirea unei\nm&#259;suri de ocrotire cu privire la mandant. Orice clauz&#259; contrar&#259;\neste considerat&#259; nescris&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_716714342\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1056\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_716714342\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Persoana care îl substituie pe mandatar este\nobligat&#259; s&#259; anun&#355;e de îndat&#259; instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;\ndespre substituire.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SUBSEC&#354;IUNEA 4:Încetarea mandatului</span></b></p>"}